content: This is the first lesson on our second opening cycle.
The purpose of Theory Department is to help new students to learn renju opening theory as well as to help old students to refresh their memory.
tunnet is fast when claire is not here :)
Today we will begin with i6 opening.It is called 'Cloud Moon'.
tunnet99, tieuphilac, Ando, pantrike, luwenzhe, Chancewu, L8RG8R, slamduk, Cloud, eastmen, yyfcsd, amitabha, guminzhao, Alan, dadisheng, moocheng.
In most cases (maybe 95%) black wins in this opening.
But if you do not know how black must play in this opening, then you will have very big problems as black.
This opening is usually set by players who like gambling style - they prepare traps in some variant and they hope that the black player is not prepared for this and falls into trap.
In this opening there are 4 different ways for white's 4th move.
The possible choices for white are: h9, g8,j8, h7.
Other 4th moves are not serious and black can win very easily.
